{"tid":1327003,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"新手一問 關於頭盔眼罩","createTime":"2019-07-17T12:14:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T12:26:43.000Z","uid":191796,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"09dfbc684df7b12821ecf5dd5a71c41186224bf6","tid":1327003,"uid":191796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T12:14:20.000Z","msg":"嚟緊721就到 所以小弟今日收工都走左去買定個頭盔同眼罩 但買完先發覺有啲疑問 如果覺得我問啲問題好白癡低能 盡量屌得輕手啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 想知係咪到金鐘嗰一刻就笠晒啲嘢 定係遊行開始先笠 因為我諗緊如果一出閘俾狗查到個袋有呢啲嘢 又唔知應該點解釋好<br />\n<br />\n2. 如果完左嗰日 係咪要將啲頭盔眼罩掉晒佢 因為之前睇過post都有話驚俾人秋後算帳 所以掉晒為妙 但我又覺得可以為物資出一分力 咁如果完左唔想帶返屋企想捐出黎做物資又可以俾邊個？<br />\n<br />\n原諒我第一次開post 1999<br />\nbtw 721金鐘見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65c9389c3c59a22b3c3a3e2f75990957246aea40","tid":1327003,"uid":191796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T12:15:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"173c8e95186ef18b80954b7f68ff9d920fc093ff","tid":1327003,"uid":81385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T12:16:14.000Z","msg":"1. 我冇野講<br />\n2. 前線有物資站，急救站，比哂佢地後你好閃人，冇裝不宜久留"},{"pid":"4c7b842d76db5269ac7f9ea70a0c77b27fe6fb5a","tid":1327003,"uid":278392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T12:17:36.000Z","msg":"2.前線有人需要可以傳上去"},{"pid":"7493ce1928758c267b7a7639367860ebf8c9561d","tid":1327003,"uid":191796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"173c8e95186ef18b80954b7f68ff9d920fc093ff","tid":1327003,"uid":81385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T12:16:14.000Z","msg":"1. 我冇野講<br />\n2. 前線有物資站，急救站，比哂佢地後你好閃人，冇裝不宜久留"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T12:18:44.000Z","msg":"如果我冇野講完佢都唔放我走 話懷疑我做暴徒咁點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d71aa8999988146087039dd9af3b46c3b